{"id":145410,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：莫少聪孙兴涉毒品北京被捕/","date":"2011-04-18T13:30:42Z","modified":"2011-04-18T13:30:42Z","title":"简讯：莫少聪孙兴涉毒品北京被捕","content":"<div>\n<p>香港艺人莫少聪和孙兴分别因吸毒和藏毒被北京警方逮捕。</p>\n<p>据曾到派出所探望二人的香港艺人透露，莫少聪和孙兴是上周五（15日）被捕的。</p>\n<p>他引警方透露的消息称，莫少聪仅涉吸毒，可能被监禁三日即会获释。</p>\n<p>而由于警方在孙兴家中发现毒品，他将被关押至少15天。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-K2GvFD-PAlKclg08mRmyQxnZ8s/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-K2GvFD-PAlKclg08mRmyQxnZ8s/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-K2GvFD-PAlKclg08mRmyQxnZ8s/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-K2GvFD-PAlKclg08mRmyQxnZ8s/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/4noz-4cvfk8\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=752465\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}